# 🌱 Spring Boot & Spring Core Examples

This repository contains practice programs and examples demonstrating the fundamentals of **Spring Core** and **Spring Boot**. It includes examples of dependency injection, annotations, configuration, repository/service layers, Java Streams, and REST API development.

---

## 📌 Topics Covered

- ✅ Spring Core
- ✅ Spring Boot Basics
- ✅ Dependency Injection (DI)
- ✅ Spring Annotations
- ✅ Java Configuration
- ✅ Repository & Service Layer
- ✅ Java Stream API
- ✅ REST API Basics
- ✅ Postman API Testing

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
├── App.java
├── AppConfig.java
├── AppTest.java
├── StudentRepository.java
├── StudentService.java
├── StreamBasics.java
├── StreamFunctions.java
├── StreamFunctionsDemo.java
├── StreamApiDemo.java
├── Cn_Flight.java
└── SpringBoot with PostMan Code Example.zip
```

